Heap - a heap must be a complete binary tree.
It is of two type -
1. min heap - here, the root data must be small or equal then its left and right child
2. max heap - here , the root data must be greater or equal then its left and right

Heap is implemented using ArrayList.

parent index - (currentIndex - 1) / 2 ;
left child  - (2*pi)+1;
right child - (2*pi)+2;
